details

Build 3-in-1 fun in the sun with LEGO Creator 3-in-1 Seaside House. Every builder's dream true, this set comes with all the creative details you need to make your seaside dreamscape. 2-story interior with opening roof, removable top floor, double doors, and more. Plus, a surfer figure, seagull, crab, and even a fish to lay on the grill.

  • Manufacturer's Suggested Age: 7 Years and Up

  • Includes: Toy Building Components

  • Number of Pieces: 415

  • Material: Plastic

  • Educational Focus: Creative Thinking

  • Languages: English, French, Spanish

  • Dimensions: 2.4 " H x 11.1 " W x 18.9 " L

  • Product Weight: 2.26 Lb.

  • Care and Cleaning: Wipe Clean With a Dry Cloth

  • Battery: no battery used
